*Luče* se svetlost u kuću. (The light streams into the house.)

*Luka* je bila puna ribara. (The harbor was full of fishermen.)

Nisu primetili *luku* na granici. (They didn't notice the customs post at the border.)

On se *lučio* od svojih prijatelja. (He said goodbye to his friends.)

*Lukom* je pogodio metu. (He hit the target with the bow.)